description: Jake Lyons and Ryan Matthews enjoy the outdoors, and they also happen to love getting physical and horse playing.Today is no different. We caught the two messing around, wrestling and whatnot out in the garden. What they didn't expect was us to be recording their whole adventure, including the point where they stopped wrestling and began making out, which lead to getting naked and eventually fucking.Yeah, these two know how to have fun.Enjoy!
title: Horseplay
